javax.mvc.event

Interface MvcEvent

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AfterControllerEvent, AfterProcessViewEvent, BeforeControllerEvent, BeforeProcessViewEvent, ControllerRedirectEvent

    public interface MvcEvent

    Base type for all Jakarta MVC events. Every Jakarta MVC event type must extend this interface.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
